text: The Manchurian gudgeon (Gnathopogon strigatus) is a species of ray-finned fish in the genus Gnathopogon found in the Amur drainage in Russia, China, Korea, and Mongolia. ==References== Category:Gnathopogon Category:Cyprinid fish of Asia Category:Freshwater fish of China Category:Fish described in 1908
title: Manchurian gudgeon
